Class Image

  • java.lang.Object
    • Image
  • public class Image
extends java.lang.Object
    Simple class that holds 3 priority queue inside it. One priority queue holds values with respect to lexical comparison. Other priority queue holds values with respect to L2 norm values. Other priority queue holds values with respect to Bitmix comparison. It also has remove and insert methods inside it.
